fields.title: Orange - Petals
fields.description: In preparing citrus for slicing, we cut off the ends. In the spirit of letting nothing go to waste, we discovered the perfect sized garnish for smaller cocktail glasses, like the classic Nick & Nora. When dehydrated, these resemble dried flower petals, and make wonderful finishes to an egg white cocktail, punch bowl, or tea cup presentation. While they are small, they still pack in all the aromatics of the citrus.
